job_history.work_description: Lead group and private classes, administer guests' Test In and Test Outs using the InBody machine, and provide VO2 Max and/or RMR testing.
Manage office accounting and insurance billing, schedule appointments, and provide fitness training to clients.
Provide massage therapy services to clients, maintain a clean and serene massage therapy room, and advertise for the business.
Train and compete in triathlons, work with performance experts in track and field, swimming, and cycling.
Set up tables and stations for service, answer phone calls, make reservations, and seat guests.
Sell, manage, and update memberships for the gym, make phone calls and meetings with new and existing members.
